# 2.2 Aykr Deer Analizi (IQR)

import numpy as np

Q1 = X.quantile(0.25)
Q3 = X.quantile(0.75)
IQR = Q3 - Q1

upper_bound = Q3 + 1.5 * IQR

outlier_mask = (X < lower_bound) | (X > upper_bound)
outlier_counts = outlier_mask.sum()

# 7. Validation Performanslarnn llmesi

from sklearn.metrics import (
    accuracy_score,
    precision_score,
    recall_score,
    f1_score,
    roc_auc_score
)

val_results = []
trained_models = {}

for name, model in models.items():
    print(f"\n{name} eitiliyor...")
    model.fit(X_train, y_train)
    trained_models[name] = model

    y_val_pred = model.predict(X_val)
    y_val_proba = model.predict_proba(X_val)[:, 1]

    acc = accuracy_score(y_val, y_val_pred)
    prec = precision_score(y_val, y_val_pred)
    rec = recall_score(y_val, y_val_pred)
    f1 = f1_score(y_val, y_val_pred)
    roc_auc = roc_auc_score(y_val, y_val_proba)

    val_results.append({
        "Model": name,
        "Accuracy": acc,
        "Precision": prec,
        "Recall": rec,
        "F1-Score": f1,
        "ROC-AUC": roc_auc
    })

val_results_df = pd.DataFrame(val_results)
print("\nValidation Sonu Tablosu:\n")
display(val_results_df.sort_values(by="F1-Score", ascending=False))

# 8.2.1 Tm Modeller iin Confusion Matrix Grselletirmesi

from sklearn.metrics import confusion_matrix
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import seaborn as sns
import numpy as np

model_names = list(trained_models.keys())
n_models = len(model_names)

# Maksimum 6 model iin 2x3 grid; bizde 5 model var, ideal
cols = 3
rows = int(np.ceil(n_models / cols))

plt.figure(figsize=(5 * cols, 4 * rows))

for idx, name in enumerate(model_names):
    model = trained_models[name]
    y_test_pred = model.predict(X_test)
    cm = confusion_matrix(y_test, y_test_pred)

    ax = plt.subplot(rows, cols, idx + 1)
    sns.heatmap(cm, annot=True, fmt="d", cmap="Blues", cbar=False, ax=ax)
    ax.set_title(name)
    ax.set_xlabel("Tahmin Edilen Snf")
    ax.set_ylabel("Gerek Snf")

plt.suptitle("Tm Modeller iin Confusion Matrix Karlatrmas", y=1.02, fontsize=14)

# 9.1 Optuna Objective Fonksiyonu
import optuna
from sklearn.neural_network import MLPClassifier
from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score, precision_score, recall_score, f1_score, roc_auc_score

optuna.logging.set_verbosity(optuna.logging.WARNING)  # Colab ekrann temiz tutmak iin

def objective(trial):
    # 9.2 Gncel Optuna API ile parametreler
    n_hidden1 = trial.suggest_int("hidden_layer_1", 16, 256)
    n_hidden2 = trial.suggest_int("hidden_layer_2", 8, 128)
    hidden_layer_sizes = (n_hidden1, n_hidden2)

    #  GNCEL Optuna API
    learning_rate_init = trial.suggest_float(
        "learning_rate_init", 1e-5, 1e-1, log=True
    )
    alpha = trial.suggest_float(
        "alpha", 1e-6, 1e-2, log=True
    )

    activation = trial.suggest_categorical("activation", ["relu", "tanh"])
    solver = trial.suggest_categorical("solver", ["adam", "sgd"])
    batch_size = trial.suggest_categorical("batch_size", [16, 32, 64, 128])

    # MLP Modeli
    model = MLPClassifier(
        hidden_layer_sizes=hidden_layer_sizes,
        activation=activation,
        learning_rate_init=learning_rate_init,
        alpha=alpha,
        solver=solver,
        batch_size=batch_size,
        max_iter=300,
        random_state=42
    )

    # Eitim
    model.fit(X_train, y_train)

    # Validation Tahmin
    y_val_pred = model.predict(X_val)
    y_val_proba = model.predict_proba(X_val)[:, 1]

    # Metrikler
    acc = accuracy_score(y_val, y_val_pred)
    prec = precision_score(y_val, y_val_pred)
    rec = recall_score(y_val, y_val_pred)
    f1 = f1_score(y_val, y_val_pred)
    roc_auc = roc_auc_score(y_val, y_val_proba)

    # Trial loglarnn kaydedilmesi
    log_entry = {
        "trial_number": trial.number,
        "hidden_layer_1": n_hidden1,
        "hidden_layer_2": n_hidden2,
        "learning_rate_init": learning_rate_init,
        "alpha": alpha,
        "activation": activation,
        "solver": solver,
        "batch_size": batch_size,
        "val_accuracy": acc,
        "val_precision": prec,
        "val_recall": rec,
        "val_f1": f1,
        "val_roc_auc": roc_auc
    }
    optuna_trial_logs.append(log_entry)

    # Optuna ii kullanc metrii
    trial.set_user_attr("val_f1", f1)

    # Objective iin geri dn (F1 optimizasyonu)
    return f1

1. Veri Seti Hazrl ve Kalite Kontrolleri

1.1 Veri Setinin Yklenmesi

Colab ortamna yklenen breast_cancer_wisconsin.csv dosyas Pandas ile DataFramee aktarlmtr. Bamsz deikenler X, baml deiken (hedef snf) y olarak ayrlmtr.

Toplam rnek says: 569 Toplam zellik says: 30

1.2 Eksik Deer Analizi

Notebook ktsna gre veri setinde hibir stunda eksik deer yoktur (0 missing). Bu, veri setinin temiz olduunu ve ek imputasyon gerektirmediini gstermektedir.

1.3 Aykr Deer Analizi

IQR yntemine gre toplam 608 aykr deer tespit edilmitir. Bu aykr deerler zellikle aadaki stunlarda younlamtr:

worst area, worst radius, mean concave points,

mean area, radius error, perimeter error

Aykr deerlerin tespiti doru yaplsa da snflandrma problemlerinde MLP, leklendirme sonras bu deerlerden etkilenmedii iin veri dlama ilemine gidilmemitir.

1.4 Veri Tipleri

Tm zellikler float64, hedef stunu int64 trndedir. Saysal/kategorik dalm veri seti iin beklenen yapdadr.

2. Keifsel Veri Analizi (EDA)

2.1 Temel statistikler

Her zellik iin mean, median, std, minmax, Q1Q3 deerleri hesaplanmtr. En yksek varyansl zellikler:

mean area

worst area

worst radius

Bu zelliklerin model aklamalarnda da nemli rol oynad SHAP analizinde dorulanmtr.

worst radius worst perimeter: 0.9937

mean radius mean area: 0.9874

Bu yksek korelasyon deerleri, tmr boyutuna bal metriklerin birbirini gl ekilde temsil ettiini gstermektedir.

2.3 Boxplot Analizleri

Boxplotlara gre tmr bykl ile ilikili zelliklerde ok sayda aykr deer grlmtr. Bu durum, kt huylu (malignant) tmrlerde deerlerin geni aralkta deimesinden kaynaklanmaktadr.

3. Veri leklendirme

Tm zellikler StandardScaler ile leklendirilmitir. Hem MLP hem de Optuna modelleri bu lekli veriler zerine kurulmutur.
